{"tid":1992424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"限聚令下重開室外運動場　林鄭強調體育館暫不開放","createTime":"2020-04-28T06:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T06:48:12.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a211942e5785ca8372f8d8eef05b392d404e7dd7","tid":1992424,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"康文署在上月27日起全面關閉免費戶外設施，各區被膠帶圍封的室外場地成了香港一道奇特的風景。林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前說，因連續第二天未有新增病例，其他日子的個案亦只有單位數字，表示下周一（4日）起將分兩階段回復政府正常運作，第一階段絕大部分政府僱員恢復上班，公共設施在不違反限聚令下，回復開放使用，如室外運動場地、圖書館、博物館等。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/466509/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E9%A4%A8%E6%9A%AB%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F466509%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%259A%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=abb97b99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/466509/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E9%A4%A8%E6%9A%AB%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE</a>"},{"pid":"7a0ea71a2cc892c92397c8f9de53b7e6fd09ea61","tid":1992424,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:48:12.000Z","msg"